Description: Static C++ and Python utility that resolves ROS2 message numeric constants to their symbolic names (and vice-versa) by reading .msg / .srv / .action files directly from the ament_index at runtime.
 Includes enum_echo: a CLI tool to subscribe to any topic and display messages with numeric constants decoded to their symbolic names.
